title: 2011 Landcruiser Sahara
main_description: This immaculate Sahara has been set up for comfortable touring and in close to new condition with an immaculate interior and exterior. 2nd owner from 35K (kids grown up, empty back seats), this vehicle has had an ideal balance of city and country kilometres. Used to tow a hybrid camper when travelling and garaged when at home, as its condition shows.Over $10k's in extras make this vehicle an exceptional touring car as per accessories fitted in the Project 200 vehicle, copy the link or Google Project 200 to see what you are getting: https://www.project200.com.au/chip-and-exhaust/A new cruiser has arrived so this Sahara needs a new loving home!- Pearl white duco / styish beige interior- Usual Sahara features: centre console fridge, rev camera, roof DVD, sunroof, power leather seats, steering wheel controls, woodgrain finishes, electric steering adjustment etc etc- 7 seater with the larger 140 litre tank- ECB alloy bull bar with light bar- Unichip Q, a high end plug in performance upgrade that boosts power / torque whilst retaining the factory parametres for safe operation (187kw/480nm, dyno report available) with a programmed EGR delete from 40k km's- Richards transmission lock up kit ‚Äì A brilliant towing enhancement, saves fuel, lowers transmission temps and prevents overdrive dropping in and out.- Red Back 3‚Äù full length twin exhaust with noise level options- Safari Armax snorkel- BFG all terrain tyres, front tyres new October 2020, rear at about 50% tread- LED front end light upgrade- Concealed UHF with hi gain aerial- Upgraded Tough Dog springs and shocks fitted 05/2019- Air Bag Man rear air bags with kevlar sleeves- Tow Pro electric brakes- 3 rd auxiliary battery with Redarc DC-DC charger providing power to a fridge in the car and with an Anderson plug providing power to your camper / caravan- Ultragauge: engine / trans monitor for all available engine sensors- Full log books / servicing receipts available and serviced in excess of the recommended Toyota service intervals, last service Oct 2020- Licenced till March 2020

Its amazingly affordable   Access is a secured car loan that gives you lower monthly repayments and the certainty of a Guaranteed Future Value equal to the final repayment on your Toyota Certified Pre-Owned Vehicle.   Toyota Access gives you the freedom to choose the car you want today and decide whether to trade, keep or return it at the end of your loan. It?s the smart way to buy a Toyota, for both individuals and businesses.   Choose your deposit amount, loan term and the number of kilometres you expect to travel, then well calculate the Guaranteed Future Value of your new Toyota.   This calculation assumes your Toyota is kept in good condition** and stays within the agreed kilometres over the life of the loan. The GFV becomes your final payment on the loan. When your loan term ends, it?s up to you what to do next.
